title: BackgroundLogic
content:
Welcome!

Hi, I'm BackgroundLogic welcome to my garden. It's a place where I can organize my digital footprint and share things I've created. It's still evolving but I hope you find what you're looking for here.
Background Around
Github - Where I share code I've written and where I host this website.
@BackgroundLogic.bsky.social - Because Twitter is owned by a Nazi now.
Background Cooks - A digital cookbook where I post all my favorite recipes.
